domain.locations

Class Exit

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.locations.Exit

  • public class Exit
extends java.lang.Object
    An exit from on room/location to another. This is used to map out the positions of the Rooms and Locations.
    See Also:
    LocationsController.createLocations()
